{title: Blowin' in the Wind}
{artist: Bob Dylan}
{key: G}
{capo: 7}
{tempo: 90}
{duration: 2:48}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
How [G]many [C]roads must a [G]man walk [D]down
Before you [G]call him a [C]man? [D]
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
